Caglar Caliskan - Points

Caglar Caliskan scores a career high 7 points (2017)

On September 30, 2017, Caglar Caliskan set his career high in points in a Poland - 1 Liga game. That day he scored 7 points in KK Warszawa's road loss against Rawlplug Sokól Lańcut, 85-71. He also had 1 rebound. He shot 2/3 from two, 1/3 from three, shooting at 50.0% from the field.

Caglar Caliskan - Rebounds

Caglar Caliskan grabs a career high 5 rebounds (2017)

On November 19, 2017, Caglar Caliskan set his career high in rebounds in a Poland - 1 Liga game. That day he grabbed 5 rebounds in KK Warszawa's road loss against Pogoń Prudnik, 77-63. He also had 3 points, 3 assists, 2 steals.
